1. Install new theme:

- Open browser
- type "localhost/abc/wp-admin" and press enter
	username: admin
	password: admin
	click on "Log In" button

- Go to "Apprence"--> Theme
- click on "Add New" button
- click on search box and type "your theme name"
	- select your theme
	- click on "Install" button
	- click on "Active" button


2. See how new theme change your website

- Open browser
- type "localhost/abc" and press enter


Another way you can install theme
---------------------------------------------
1. Download Theme

- Open browser
- type "wordpress.org" and press enter
- select which theme you need
	- click on its "Download" button
	- copy downloaded theme
	- go to htdocs --> abc --> wp-content --> themes --> paste --> Extert here
- Active Theme:
	- Open browser
	- type "localhost/abc/wp-admin" and press enter
	- go to "Apperence" --> Themes
	- refresh page
	- select your theme and click on "Active" button

2. See how new theme change your website

- Open browser
- type "localhost/abc" and press enter


